eu.trentorise.smartcampus.osm.android.views.safecanvas

Class SafeTranslatedPath

  • java.lang.Object
    • Path
      • eu.trentorise.smartcampus.osm.android.views.safecanvas.SafeTranslatedPath

  • public class SafeTranslatedPath
extends Path
    The SafeTranslatedPath class is designed to work in conjunction with SafeTranslatedCanvas to work around various Android issues with large canvases. For the two classes to work together, call onDrawCycleStart(eu.trentorise.smartcampus.osm.android.views.safecanvas.ISafeCanvas) at the start of the Overlay#drawSafe method of your Overlay. This will set the adjustment needed to draw your Path safely on the canvas without any drawing distortion at high zoom levels. Methods of the Path class that use unsafe float types have been deprecated in favor of replacement methods that use doubles.
    Author:
    Marc Kurtz
    See Also:
    ISafeCanvas}
